
{ Install IrfanView

code {
→ Windows/dirs/ProgramData/chocolatey/bin/choco_exe[choco] install irfanview
code }

}
{ Change background color

  Press `p` or use Options->Properties.

  Choose *Viewing*

  Click into button *Choose* right of *Main window color*.

}
{ Linux equivalent

  A sort-of → Linux equivalent for IrfanView might be → design/graphic/gthumb.

}
sa:

  → Windows/dirs/Users/username/AppData/Roaming/IrfanView

  → design/graphic
